@startuml Server_CRC

title Server — CRC Diagram

class Server {
  == Responsibilities ==
  Listen for incoming TCP connections on port 5001
  Spawn a ClientHandler thread per accepted connection
  Maintain the list of all currently connected clients
  Broadcast a message to every connected client
  Remove a client from the list upon disconnect
  --
  == Collaborators ==
  ClientHandler
}

class ClientHandler {
  (collaborator)
}

Server "1" *-- "0..*" ClientHandler : spawns / manages >

@enduml
